text: On May 1, 2017, Tax Exempt and Government Entities underwent a reorganization. The new Compliance, Planning & Classiﬁcation function absorbed several employees previously housed in Federal State and Local Governments, and accepted ownership of this manual. The new IRM 4.70.6, TE/GE Examinations, Classiﬁcation & Case Assignment Procedures, supersedes this manual.
This supersedes IRM 4.90.5, Case Selection Procedures, dated November 20,
